          "original": "Samples with a relative density exceeding 99.9% were fabricated under laser power of 300 W, scanning velocity of 1200 mm/s, hatch spacing of 0.1 mm, and layer thickness of 40 μm. Two types of samples were selected: those in the as-fabricated (AF) condition...",
